title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 28 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 28 2022
description:
Texas Governor Abbott joins Clay and Buck with the latest on illegals found dead in tractor-trailer at the border: "These deaths are on Joe Biden," impeach Mayorkas, and an update on Uvalde. Abbott: Biden has stifled domestic oil production. C&B take a Savannah caller on Clarence Thomas. Kamala Harris reveals she’s "the daughter of a woman, and the granddaughter of a woman." Republican candidate for governor Rep. Lee Zeldin joins C&B to make his pitch on primary day in New York.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
